events will be carried out by the National Library of Estonia, the National Heritage Board, Estonian Public Broadcasting and the Estonian Film Foundation.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cp\u003EThe Year of Digital Culture will be defined by new approaches to reusing and rethinking our cultural heritage, as well as to resolving problems related to copyrights and open data. A Loometiiger (Creative Tiger) programme will introduce digital creativity to the younger generation, and better policies will be drafted for the analysis of cultural big data. Attention will also be paid to the flip side of the digital world, for example, digital addiction, identity theft and cyber security.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C\/div\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003C\/div\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\u003C\/div\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022column grid-3\u0022\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022grid-inner\u0022\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003Ch2\u003EThe Year of Digital Culture\u003C\/h2\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cul class=\u0022widget-menu\u0022\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cli\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/medium.com\/the-story-of-digital-culture-in-estonia\u0022\u003EThe website of\u0026nbsp;the Year of Digital Culture\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cli\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/digikultuur\/\u0022\u003EFacebook page of the Year of Digital Culture\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cli\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C\/ul\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003C\/div\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\u003C\/div\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022column grid-3\u0022\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022grid-inner\u0022\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003Ch2\u003ETheme-years\u003C\/h2\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cul class=\u0022widget-menu\u0022\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cli\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022\/en\/theme-years\/future-theme-years\u0022\u003EFuture theme years\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cli\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022\/en\/previous-theme-years\u0022\u003EPrevious theme years\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cli\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C\/ul\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003C\/div\u003E\r\n\t\t\t\u003C\/div\u003E\r\n\t\t\u003C\/div\u003E\r\n\t\u003C\/div\u003E\r\n\u003C\/div\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv id=\u0022menu-l2-popup-menu-mlid-7831\u0022 class=\u0022menu-l2-popup menu-mlid menu-mlid-7831\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022arrow\u0022\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E","mobile_navigation":{"breakpoint":"all and (min-width:720px)","menuSelector":"div.block-main-menu div.menu-block-wrapper","menuPlugin":"accordion","showEffect":"expand_down","showItems":"active_trail","tabHandler":1,"menuWidth":"100","specialClasses":0,"mainPageSelector":"#page","useMask":0},"googleanalytics":{"trackOutbound":1,"trackMailto":1,"trackDownload":1,"trackDownloadExtensions":"7z|aac|arc|arj|asf|asx|avi|bin|csv|doc(x|m)?|dot(x|m)?|exe|flv|gif|gz|gzip|hqx|jar|jpe?g|js|mp(2|3|4|e?g)|mov(ie)?|msi|msp|pdf|phps|png|ppt(x|m)?|pot(x|m)?|pps(x|m)?|ppam|sld(x|m)?|thmx|qtm?|ra(m|r)?|sea|sit|tar|tgz|torrent|txt|wav|wma|wmv|wpd|xls(x|m|b)?|xlt(x|m)|xlam|xml|z|zip","trackColorbox":1},"urlIsAjaxTrusted":{"\/en\/news\/measures-mitigate-impact-covid-19-virus-outbreak-culture-and-audiovisual-sector-estonia":true},"omega":{"layouts":{"primary":"desktop","order":["tablet","desktop"],"queries":{"tablet":"screen and (min-device-width: 768px) and (max-device-width: 1023px)","desktop":"screen and (min-device-width: 1024px)"}}}});
