e-2020-and-museums">Culture 2020 and museums</a></li><li class="last leaf menu-mlid-7789" id="menu-mlid-7789"><a href="/en/activities/museums/state-indemnity-exhibitions">State Indemnity for Exhibitions</a></li></ul></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-5972" id="menu-mlid-5972"><a href="/en/activities/music">Music</a></li><li class="last expanded menu-mlid-5935" id="menu-mlid-5935"><a href="/en/activities/sport">Sport</a><ul class="menu"><li class="first last leaf menu-mlid-7826" id="menu-mlid-7826"><a href="/en/activities/sport/changes-principles-financing-sports">Changes in principles of financing sports</a></li></ul></li></ul></li><li class="expanded menu-mlid-5887" id="menu-mlid-5887"><a href="/en/node/14248">News</a><ul class="menu"><li class="first leaf menu-mlid-5014" id="menu-mlid-5014"><a href="/en/news">News</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-5018" id="menu-mlid-5018"><a href="/en/galleries">Galleries</a></li><li class="last leaf menu-mlid-7759" id="menu-mlid-7759"><a href="http://www.kul.ee/en/contact">Communication Department</a></li></ul></li><li class="expanded menu-mlid-5937" id="menu-mlid-5937"><a href="/en/node/14252">Organisation</a><ul class="menu"><li class="first leaf menu-mlid-6502" id="menu-mlid-6502"><a href="https://www.kul.ee/en/minister-culture-tonis-lukas">Minister of Culture Tõnis Lukas</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-7819" id="menu-mlid-7819"><a href="/en/secretary-general-tarvi-sits">Secretary General Tarvi Sits</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-5946" id="menu-mlid-5946"><a href="/en/organisation/directorate">Directorate</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-7757" id="menu-mlid-7757"><a href="http://www.kul.ee/en/contact">All contacts</a></li><li class="last leaf menu-mlid-5942" id="menu-mlid-5942"><a href="/en/organisation/introduction-ministry">Overview and structure</a></li></ul></li><li class="has-separator expanded menu-mlid-7613" id="menu-mlid-7613"><a href="/en/node/16433" class="has-separator">Theme years</a><ul class="menu"><li class="first leaf menu-mlid-7615" id="menu-mlid-7615"><a href="/en/theme-years/future-theme-years">Future theme-years</a></li><li class="last leaf menu-mlid-7614" id="menu-mlid-7614"><a href="/en/theme-years/year-childrens-and-youth-culture-2017">The Year of Children’s and Youth Culture 2017</a></li></ul></li><li class="otselink last expanded menu-mlid-7831" id="menu-mlid-7831"><a href="/en/node/18840" class="otselink">COVID-19 crisis webpage</a><ul class="menu"><li class="otselink first last leaf menu-mlid-7848" id="menu-mlid-7848"><a href="https://www.kriis.ee/en" class="otselink" target="_blank">Emergency situation</a></li></ul></li></ul></div>
